data.description: This charming 3 Br/1.5 Bath home is close to Downtown Lincolnton. Home has open floorplan concept and has been recently updated with new vinyl plank floors, new paint throughout, light fixtures and new heat pump. Front of the home is brick with vinyl on sides and back. On the outside, is a fenced backyard and a storage closet on the side of the home.  Come and see this nice home. $255,000
